danish_publication: Der var én, som skulde sidde i kirken en nat, og præsten ridsede en kreds i gulvet om hende med en lyngkrog. Hun blev fristet mange gange den nat, men de kunde ikke komme indenfor kredsen, og hun sad helt stille og sagde blot: "A priser min Gud!"
english_publication: There was one who was supposed to sit in the church for an entire night, and the minister scratched a circle in the floor around her with a lightning pole. She was tempted many times that night, but they couldn't come inside the circle, and she sat completely still and only said: "I praise my God!"
